                            <name>OFFSET0_POS</name>
                            <description>POSITIVE OFFSET THIS BIT IS SET AND CLEARED BY SOFTWARE TO ENABLE THE POSITIVE OFFSET. 0: NEGATIVE OFFSET 1: POSITIVE OFFSET
NOTE: THE SOFTWARE IS ALLOWED TO WRITE THESE BITS
ONLY WHEN ADSTART = 0 AND
JADSTART = 0 (WHICH ENSURES THAT NO CONVERSION
IS ONGOING)</description>
                            <bitOffset>17</bitOffset>
                            <bitWidth>1</bitWidth>
                        </field>
